Package ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.notifications

Class Notification

java.lang.Object
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.database.utils.DocumentSerializable
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.notifications.Notification
Direct Known Subclasses:
Milestone, sendToUserNotification
public class Notification extends DocumentSerializable
Represents a notification associated with a user event. It contains information about the notification message, the time it was generated, the creator of the notification, and the event it is associated with. Users will store references to these notifications, and the profile class contains a list of all notifications.

    • Notification

      public Notification(String message, UUID creatorID, UUID eventID)
      Constructs a new Notification with the specified message, creator's UUID, and event's UUID. It automatically sets the creation time to the current moment and generates a unique identifier for the notification.
      Parameters:
      message - the notification message content
      creatorID - the UUID of the creator of the notification
      eventID - the UUID of the event associated with the notification
